title: Hour 3 - Dan Orlovsky
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Dan Orlovsky
description:
Dan Patrick is joined by former NFL QB and current ESPN NFL analyst Dan Orlovsky to talk about the rumor that Tom Brady and Rob Gronkowski were almost members of the Raiders, before the deal was nixed at the last minute.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
